OL,3,C10,000 children in the North West will
OL,4,Cbe homeless this Christmas
OL,6,FThe charity Shelter have claimed a
OL,7,Frecord 22,000 people in the North West
OL,8,Fwill spend Christmas without a home,
OL,9,Fwith nearly half of that number being
OL,10,Fchildren.
OL,12,FMore than 360 people will be sleeping
OL,13,Frough on any given night. While more
OL,14,Fthan 20,000 people will be living in
OL,15,Ftemporary accommodation.
