OL,3,C10,000 children in the North West will
OL,4,Cbe homeless this Christmas
OL,6,FShelter's research also looks at
OL,7,Fplaces across the North West where
OL,8,Fhomelessness is most acute. Manchester
OL,9,Fhas the highest number of people
OL,10,Fwithout a home with 9,000 people
OL,11,Fhomeless, followed by Liverpool where
OL,12,Fit's 2,200 people and Salford with
OL,13,F1,900 people homeless.
OL,15,FHomeless Aid UK is a charity based in
OL,16,FBolton who have seen demand for their
OL,17,Fservices increase, particularly in the
OL,18,Frun up to Christmas.
