OL,3,C10,000 children in the North West will
OL,4,Cbe homeless this Christmas
OL,6,FBilla Ahmad started the charity in
OL,7,F2010 and runs soup kitchens and food
OL,8,Fbanks across the region, he said:
OL,9,F"Just in Bolton we've got five soup
OL,10,Fkitchens and if you are homeless then
OL,11,Fevery single day we provide food, the
OL,12,Fsituation is getting worse, a lot of
OL,13,Fnew faces and we are doing what we can
OL,14,Fbut there is not enough affordable
OL,15,Faccommodation"
OL,17,FThe team of volunteers help people
OL,18,Flike Jordan Macloud who is now in
OL,19,Fsheltered accommodation, but had lived
OL,20,Fon the streets for four years.
