OL,3,C10,000 children in the North West will
OL,4,Cbe homeless this Christmas
OL,6,FHe said: "There's many cold nights,
OL,7,Fyou sleep in doorways, you get drunk
OL,8,Fpeople messing with you and throwing
OL,9,Fthings and it isn't fun not at all"
OL,11,FSeparate figures from the Greater
OL,12,FManchester Combined authority show the
OL,13,Fnumber of people rough sleeping is
OL,14,Freducing with an extra million pounds
OL,15,Fbeing spent to help ease the pressures.
OL,17,FMayor of Greater Manchester Andy
OL,18,FBurnham has also announced a boost to
OL,19,Fbed spaces in 'A Bed Every Night'
OL,20,Faccommodation from 2025.
