OL,3,C10,000 children in the North West will
OL,4,Cbe homeless this Christmas
OL,6,FThis year Greater Manchester has
OL,7,Fincreased the number of spaces across
OL,8,FA Bed Every Night sites to 550, with
OL,9,Fadditional provision put in place by
OL,10,Fcouncils in response to urgent need.
OL,11,FThis means that on any given night,
OL,12,Fmore than 550 people are being
OL,13,Fsupported across the city-region.
OL,15,FFrom next April, the number will rise
OL,16,Fto more than 600 ` helping to provide
OL,17,Feven more support to people in need.
