OL,3,C10,000 children in the North West will
OL,4,Cbe homeless this Christmas
OL,6,FAndy Burnham said: "As we face another
OL,7,Fchallenging winter, Greater Manchester
OL,8,Fis coming together to send a clear
OL,9,Fsignal that support is available ` but
OL,10,Fthe current pressures on the system
OL,11,Fcannot be sustained.
OL,13,F"There is an urgent need to invest in
OL,14,Fservices like A Bed Every Night, so we
OL,15,Fcan bring people inside and offer them
OL,16,Fthe kind of personalised support that
OL,17,Fwill help them get back on their feet.
OL,18,FBut there is also an urgent need to
OL,19,Fget upstream and stop the flow of
OL,20,Fpeople onto our streets."
