OL,6,FThere has been an increase in people
OL,7,Fstaying in so called half way houses,
OL,8,Fno longer sleeping rough but still in
OL,9,Fneed of food and extra help.
OL,11,FJordan said: "If you look for the help
OL,12,Fthen it is there but it won't just
OL,13,Fcome to you there are plenty of
OL,14,Fservices willing to help but sometimes
OL,15,Fit's that people don't want to engage"
