OL,3,C10,000 children in the North West will
OL,4,Cbe homeless this Christmas
OL,6,FFamilies who become homeless are
OL,7,Fusually placed in temporary
OL,8,Faccommodation by their local council,
OL,9,Fbut the government's own data shows
OL,10,Fthat 23% of families in the North West
OL,11,Fhave been there for over two years.
