OL,3,C10,000 children in the North West will
OL,4,Cbe homeless this Christmas
OL,6,FJohn Ryan, Manchester Service Lead at
OL,7,FShelter, said: "We see the damage that
OL,8,Fhomelessness has on people, the trauma
OL,9,Fthat it causes. We see children
OL,10,Fmissing out on their education and
OL,11,Fhealth and wellbeing and it is not
OL,12,Fgood enough in society we need to see
OL,13,Fsocial renting and social homes being
OL,14,Fbuilt so people can get a safe and
OL,15,Fsecure home where they can thrive"
